Authority to enter into a FRAMEWORK AGREEMENT with THE ST. LAWRENCE SEAWAY
MANAGEMENT CORPORATION which provides for the transfer of responsibility
for the management and operation of the St. Lawrence Seaway to this not-
for-profit corporation comprised of users of the seaway.
